Alembic migrations live here (refactored under src/data).

Quick commands:
- Set PYTHONPATH to repo root: PYTHONPATH=$(pwd)
- Upgrade: UV_CACHE_DIR=.uv-cache uv run alembic upgrade head
- Create revision: UV_CACHE_DIR=.uv-cache uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"
- Downgrade: UV_CACHE_DIR=.uv-cache uv run alembic downgrade -1

Config:
- script_location points here in alembic.ini
- env.py loads models from src/data/models.py and settings from src/data/config.py
